flowchart TD
    Start[Consumer request] --> Auth[Auth + rate-limit]
    Auth --> Decrypt{Optional<br/>sender-seal?}
    Decrypt -->|Yes| DecryptBox[Decrypt NaCl Box]
    Decrypt -->|No| Plaintext[Plaintext in CVM]
    DecryptBox --> Plaintext
    Plaintext --> Estimate[Estimate tokens + reserve balance]
    Estimate --> QuickCheck[QuickCapacityCheck]
    QuickCheck -->|No provider| Return404[404/503/429]
    QuickCheck -->|Providers exist| Reserve[ReserveProviderEx]

    subgraph gates["Routing gates"]
        Catalog[Catalog + model fit]
        Trust[Trust floor + CodeAttested]
        Runtime[Runtime verified]
        Challenge[Fresh challenge < 6 min]
        Traits[Vision / tools / version]
        Cooldown[Error / memory cooldowns]
    end

    Reserve --> gates
    gates --> Cost[Cost-minimization selection]
    Cost --> Encrypt[Encrypt to provider X25519]
    Encrypt --> Dispatch[Dispatch inference_request]

    style gates fill:#e3f2fd
